Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:09.47,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}手を伸ばして　焦がれていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.05,0:01:13.55,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}届くはずない　光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:17.51,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}こんな世界で　こんな世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:20.10,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}何度も見てた夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.61,0:01:31.69,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}君の割れた　硝子細工
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:35.41,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur4}触れた指が　痛いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:39.66,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}大切なもの　要らないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:42.48,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}元には戻せない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:47.34,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愛　一雫　頬を濡らして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:50.26,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}切なく　雨が降る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:55.67,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}まだ何も君を知らないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:59.72,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}その涙が　止まったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:03.52,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}笑ってみてほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:07.86,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}あ憧れて　憧れて　想像を形へと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:11.72,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}変えるリアリティ　空を駆けて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:16.00,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}行くよ　窓の外は君を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:17.91,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}連れ出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:20.47,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}真っ暗な雲が去って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:25.05,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}残した水面に　映る色は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.05,0:02:31.67,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨上がり　君は　君の目で答えを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:34.80,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}探してほしい
Comment: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:06.43,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,OP-CN
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:09.47,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我所伸出的手　如此急不可耐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.05,0:01:13.55,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}那所无法传达　光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:17.51,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}在如此的天地里　在这样的世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:20.10,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}浮生若梦　回眸几何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.61,0:01:31.69,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}你所制作的　玻璃饰品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:35.41,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur4}指尖一触　寸心如割
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:39.66,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}必不可少的　不再所需的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:42.48,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}至始至终　覆水难收
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:47.34,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}爱　仅需一滴　脸颊便能浸润
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:50.26,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}心如刀绞　雨恨云愁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:55.67,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我还是对你　一无所知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:59.72,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那些落泪　就此止泣的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:03.52,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}多想与你　欢声笑语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:07.86,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如此憧憬　如此向往　想象便形成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:11.72,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就能改变当下　于晴空翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:16.00,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一起出发吧　窗外的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:17.91,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}携手与你共赏春秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:20.47,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}黑云已散　风光日霁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:25.05,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨后镜花水月　依旧彩虹色映
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.05,0:02:31.67,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨过天晴的你　眼眸自知物理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:34.80,Yuri004-OP-CHS,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不过我想让你　所寻自己而已
Comment: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:36.14,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,0,0,,ED-JP
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.94,0:22:25.54,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}寄り添う　二人の物語
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.54,0:22:31.11,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}色を付け道になり　交ざり合う
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.11,0:22:34.82,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}満ち足り　欠けたり
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.82,0:22:36.98,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}繰り返しながら
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.98,0:22:40.82,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}抱え込んだ昨日さえ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.82,0:22:42.60,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愛してゆこう
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.60,0:22:45.62,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}重なる　メロディーが
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.62,0:22:47.86,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}明日も　ずっと
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.86,0:22:50.58,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}続きますように
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.58,0:22:56.80,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}願い込めた空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:00.60,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}君の声が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:03.52,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}聞こえるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.52,0:23:06.39,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}この歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.39,0:23:09.15,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}響かせよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:11.32,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}どんな時でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:13.53,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}二人で　乘り越えてゆ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.53,0:23:18.30,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}こう譲れない絆を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.30,0:23:25.41,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}かけがえのない　君だから
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.79,0:23:31.21,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Only for you
Comment: 0,0:22:04.94,0:22:04.94,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,0,0,0,,ED-CHS
Dialogue: 2,0:22:19.94,0:22:25.54,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}形影相依　一段二人物语
Dialogue: 2,0:22:25.54,0:22:31.11,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}行路色彩艳丽　交织一起
Dialogue: 2,0:22:31.11,0:22:34.82,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}是我心满意足　还是不足
Dialogue: 2,0:22:34.82,0:22:36.98,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}旧事循环往复　如此而已
Dialogue: 2,0:22:36.98,0:22:40.82,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}相拥于怀　不过昨日记忆
Dialogue: 2,0:22:40.82,0:22:42.60,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}让我们一起　坠入爱河里
Dialogue: 2,0:22:42.60,0:22:45.62,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}重波叠浪　音律乐章
Dialogue: 2,0:22:45.62,0:22:47.86,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}明天也要　直到永远
Dialogue: 2,0:22:47.86,0:22:50.58,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}但愿海枯石烂
Dialogue: 2,0:22:50.58,0:22:56.80,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}也要实现飞天的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:00.60,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}你的心声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:03.52,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我能听到呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.52,0:23:06.39,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}这首旋律啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.39,0:23:09.15,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}于我心中回响
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:11.32,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}无论何时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:13.53,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}两人一起　乘风破浪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.53,0:23:18.30,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}这份坚不可摧的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.30,0:23:25.41,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}独一无二不可替代　是因为你呀
Dialogue: 2,0:23:26.79,0:23:31.21,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}只为你一人呀
